{"tid":2123333,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做過美心閪餅？","createTime":"2020-07-24T14:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T13:17:23.000Z","uid":49128,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c15467b9451fbd7c21ab48a2150e7232d8dc691a","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"暑期工時做過pt<br />\n<br />\n閪撚到爆，d員工飯又難食<br />\n<br />\n去過廁所都要批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n番工放工搭專車，話就話番9.5個鐘，搭埋車來回都12-13個鐘<br />\n<br />\n仲要食飯得半個鐘，仲要唔計錢（做pt唔係炒散）<br />\n<br />\n即係9個鐘錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作環境垃圾，仲好易燙傷（出麵包）<br />\n<br />\n做左幾日頂唔順走撚左<br />\n<br />\n仲要d同事睇落弱智咁，番工想搵個正常人吹水都冇，日子好撚難捱<br />\n<br />\n仲慘撚過入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手板眼見功夫不斷重複做，冇得停冇水吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話唔比帶電話入工場，都onlun9，邊個後生仔番工唔禁電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2abcb51f89748d4e9bd212e7b824265b0a12f6","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"唔好話正常人<br />\n<br />\n輕度弱智都唔會做<br />\n<br />\n偏偏我去左番幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244d8f8415efd8c45f55d6569fa72e4624a2e142","tid":2123333,"uid":13149,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"有 個陣比高登仔呃左去做暑假工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a476dc6a82a3653c83d23e84c42232f47ab75227","tid":2123333,"uid":33359,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"以前高登好興中秋前水人入去整月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f8649d1143a8a9fa8c9db10f9b4a9b49c21fe4","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244d8f8415efd8c45f55d6569fa72e4624a2e142","tid":2123333,"uid":13149,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"有 個陣比高登仔呃左去做暑假工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"做左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be87be8c84f31f4fba831e2f4c5e543a13ea73da","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a476dc6a82a3653c83d23e84c42232f47ab75227","tid":2123333,"uid":33359,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"以前高登好興中秋前水人入去整月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"咁閪辛苦又低人工<br />\n<br />\n高登仔真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6c4c1557e7f3bb71a1534abf1d267d0771d0cb","tid":2123333,"uid":207017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"果陣挨左成個暑期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係幾好體驗<br />\n同年紀既人多，其次呀姐<br />\n間公司好系，食lunch得半個鐘，返工無咩機會休息，狂做。<br />\n好彩有個老師父帶住我地蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返生產線d女工真係好似差利卓別靈套野咁，做慢d成條生產線都會kick住"},{"pid":"6efdb8205c079638ac796a459d4151d82143c97b","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b6c4c1557e7f3bb71a1534abf1d267d0771d0cb","tid":2123333,"uid":207017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"果陣挨左成個暑期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係幾好體驗<br />\n同年紀既人多，其次呀姐<br />\n間公司好系，食lunch得半個鐘，返工無咩機會休息，狂做。<br />\n好彩有個老師父帶住我地蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返生產線d女工真係好似差利卓別靈套野咁，做慢d成條生產線都會kick住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"美心閪餅放棄曬全部年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62365160688513ef8fb26517f7d17943816df1ce","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"有人話做完美心閪餅，藍都變黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96e9960adb443fde9d18a6be2a1977756b3d568","tid":2123333,"uid":49128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"睇黎連登仔人人50k係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0cdac04519b90f52eb7dcc50292b73494e9950","tid":2123333,"uid":203250,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"覺得嗰餐飯幾好食